data.description: Well maintained 2 Story gorgeous Home got Re-roofed with GAF Architectural Shingles Only  over a  Year Ago with a fairly new AC.  1st Floor offers separate dining room, spacious living room with gas logs fireplace, kitchen have an updated granite counter tops, plenty of cabinets for storage with a walk in pantry.  New carpets installed in the 2nd Floor.  All 3 BR are in the 2nd Floor with a flexible use bonus room that can be converted into 4th Bedroom or a Loft.  Master BR have walk-in closet, tub, private toilet and enclosed glass door standing shower.  LOW HOA, NO CDD, Great Location, only 7 min away to the Shopping Center, 10 Min Away to the Airport, Near UF Health North and More. This Home has a lot to Offer!  COME HOME!!!
